channel.title: Looking to join a Team
channel.description:
Hi, I'm looking to join a Team.
Basically what I'm looking for is an active team that has inspiration to work on the project and not quit after a week or two.
What I can offer:
Basic coding experience. A .com website related to the RSPS scene. I will be active, honest, and trustworthy
If you are interested in having me on your team, add my Skype - garrett3650
P.S. - I own my own .com website and we can use it, if need be.
